  "description": "The famous cat and mouse are back in <i>Tom and Jerry Tales</i>. The story is simple: Tom's masters are out and he quickly makes a plan to catch Jerry. Jerry strikes back and the chase begins! The gameplay is also simple: the player moves Jerry and follows the chunks of cheese Tom has placed. When Jerry meets Tom or enters any hole, do whatever appears on the screen.<br><br>The adventures and chases of Tom and Jerry are shown through 2D graphics. Jerry can unlock new costumes and change his outfit. A password system allows the to continue from the last level reached. <br><br>There is a <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/nintendo-ds/tom-and-jerry-tales_\">Nintendo DS version</a> for this game. Although they have the same name and are made by the same company, the gameplay differs between both versions.",
